WEBVTT

00:15.020 --> 00:16.460
CHAPTER III

00:17.380 --> 00:23.640
And unto the angel of the church in Sardis write, These things saith he that hath the

00:23.640 --> 00:26.880
Seven Spirits of God and the Seven Stars.

00:27.400 --> 00:32.680
I know thy works, that thou hast a name that thou livest and art dead.

00:33.440 --> 00:39.340
Be watchful and strengthen the things which remain, that are ready to die, for I have

00:39.340 --> 00:42.260
not found thy works perfect before God.

00:43.100 --> 00:48.600
Remember therefore how thou hast received and heard, and hold fast and repent.

00:48.600 --> 00:55.140
If therefore thou shalt not watch, I will come on thee as a thief, and thou shalt not

00:55.140 --> 00:57.540
know what hour I will come upon thee.

00:58.340 --> 01:04.240
Thou hast a few names even in Sardis which have not defiled their garments, and they

01:04.240 --> 01:07.620
shall walk with me in white, for they are worthy.

01:08.500 --> 01:14.900
He that overcometh the same shall be clothed in white raiment, and I will not blot out

01:14.900 --> 01:21.260
his name out of the Book of Life, but I will confess his name before my Father and before

01:21.260 --> 01:22.380
his angels.

01:23.460 --> 01:28.620
He that hath an ear, let him hear what the Spirit saith unto the churches.

01:29.800 --> 01:36.400
And to the angel of the church in Philadelphia write, These things saith he that is holy,

01:36.740 --> 01:44.740
he that is true, he that hath the key of David, he that openeth and no man shutteth, and shutteth

01:44.740 --> 01:46.460
and no man openeth.

01:47.060 --> 01:48.580
I know thy works.

01:49.080 --> 01:56.560
Behold, I have set before thee an open door, and no man can shut it, for thou hast a little

01:56.560 --> 02:01.480
strength, and hast kept my word, and hast not denied my name.

02:02.240 --> 02:08.380
Behold, I will make them of the synagogue of Satan which say they are Jews and are not,

02:08.380 --> 02:09.840
but do lie.

02:10.240 --> 02:17.200
Behold, I will make them to come and worship before thy feet, and to know that I have loved thee.

02:17.740 --> 02:24.540
Because thou hast kept the word of my patience, I also will keep thee from the hour of temptation,

02:25.080 --> 02:29.980
which shall come upon all the world to try them that dwell upon the earth.

02:30.860 --> 02:32.740
Behold, I come quickly.

02:33.320 --> 02:37.840
Hold that fast which thou hast, that no man take thy crown.

02:38.640 --> 02:45.080
Him that overcometh will I make a pillar in the temple of my God, and he shall go no more

02:45.080 --> 02:45.560
out.

02:46.020 --> 02:53.060
And I will write upon him the name of my God, and the name of the city of my God, which

02:53.060 --> 03:00.260
is New Jerusalem, which cometh down out of heaven from my God, and I will write upon

03:00.260 --> 03:02.200
him my new name.

03:02.860 --> 03:07.860
He that hath an ear, let him hear what the Spirit saith unto the churches.

03:08.840 --> 03:17.040
And unto the angel of the church of the Laodiceans write, These things saith thee Amen, the faithful

03:17.040 --> 03:21.300
and true witness, the beginning of the creation of God.

03:21.980 --> 03:26.680
I know thy works, that thou art neither cold nor hot.

03:26.680 --> 03:29.600
I would thou wert cold or hot.

03:30.000 --> 03:37.640
So then because thou art lukewarm and neither cold nor hot, I will spew thee out of my mouth,

03:38.060 --> 03:45.620
because thou sayest, I am rich and increased with goods and have need of nothing, and knowest

03:45.620 --> 03:52.340
not that thou art wretched and miserable and poor and blind and naked.

03:53.040 --> 03:59.920
I counsel thee to buy of me gold tried in the fire that thou mayest be rich, and white

03:59.920 --> 04:05.920
raiment that thou mayest be clothed, and that the shame of thy nakedness do not appear,

04:06.520 --> 04:11.060
and anoint thine eyes with eye-sav that thou mayest see.

04:11.860 --> 04:15.280
As many as I love, I rebuke and chasten.

04:16.000 --> 04:18.420
Be zealous therefore, and repent.

04:19.640 --> 04:22.640
Behold, I stand at the door and knock.

04:23.100 --> 04:29.440
If any man hear my voice and open the door, I will come in to them, and will sup with

04:29.440 --> 04:31.560
him, and he with me.

04:32.020 --> 04:38.960
To him that overcometh, will I grant to sit with me in my throne, even as I also overcame,

04:39.440 --> 04:42.540
and am set down with my father in his throne.

04:43.200 --> 04:48.740
He that hath an ear, let him hear what the Spirit saith unto the churches.

04:50.300 --> 04:52.260
The end of chapter 3.

